{"type":"text","timestamp":1783579301350,"sessionID":"ses_0ba642b18ffeuNIy0e8iZF9983","part":{"id":"prt_f459c4e7d001ROHu8MVQj2NCqn","messageID":"msg_f459c2ad7001xUX7XBrIw1L4lx","sessionID":"ses_0ba642b18ffeuNIy0e8iZF9983","type":"text","text":"```json\n{\n  \"anomaly_ids\": [],\n  \"record_ids\": [],\n  \"answer\": \"现行制度下，单笔费用报销金额达到10000元（含）以上且低于50000元时，需要部门总经理审批。根据《XX证券授权管理办法》附件二费用报销审批权限表，AR-03档位规定单笔金额大于等于10000元且小于50000元的必要审批角色为部门总经理。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"附件二 AR-03\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第五条\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```","time":{"start":1783579299453,"end":1783579301340}}}
